the frame everytime.

00:02:37.350 --> 00:02:39.530
For next time I will know to
place the camera higher.

00:02:45.790 --> 00:02:48.140
So 3 simple hairstyles for everyday.

00:02:48.230 --> 00:02:54.030
If you are going to use any of them tag me on 
FB, Twitter or Instagram so i can see them.

